skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: interesting celebrity facts
des:
This alexa skill will help you know about various celebrities around the globe. It brings you hundreds of amazing and interesting facts about celebrities which you may not be aware of. The celebrities include cricketers, bollywood stars, hollywood actors and actress, singers, directors, artists, wrestlers and many more.
 Whenever you are bored of something and want to learn something new just try this skill
For example
User: "Alexa tell interesting celebrity facts"
Alexa: "Here's your fact: Iftikhar Ali Khan Pataudi, Saif Ali Khan’s grandfather, is the only cricketer to play Test cricket for both India and England."

Prerequisites: Amazon Echo or Any Alexa enabled device.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
